statements.sql:
select `hotels`.*, (
6371 * acos(
cos(radians(null)) * cos(radians(hotels.latitude)) *
cos(radians(hotels.longitude) - radians(null)) +
sin(radians(null)) * sin(radians(hotels.latitude))
)
) AS distance from `hotels` where `hotels`.`name` LIKE '%Test Hotel%' having `distance` <= 10 order by `distance` asc limit 11 offset 0
